### Complete: 886dd44d - 07:24
Findings:
- CLI uses simple switch pattern, upgrade fits cleanly as new case
- No version tracking exists - GhostState and GhostboxConfig need imageVersion field
- ensureGhostPiAgent only copies auth if missing - needs force copy for upgrade
- init builds image but doesn't compute/store version hash
- list only gets ghost map, needs config access for stale detection
- State normalization needs backfill for new version fields
Gotchas: init writes state before build, failed wake leaves stale containerId, auth refresh needed

### Synthesis - 07:25
Approach: 9-point implementation plan covering types, hash computation, state normalization,
stamp on spawn/wake, auth refresh helper, upgrade function, CLI command, list enhancement, init update.
All changes follow existing patterns. Reuses killGhost/wakeGhost for rolling restart.

